metadata.name: Muse of Music
metadata.description:
"Muse of Music"
An amazing girl who, like no one else, understands what people who have found their meaning in life in music need. With her fragile hands and low voice, she skillfully guides mortals to the peak of their creative activity.
This is my idea of ​​these amazing divine nymphs, which do not have any specific features, because they are different for each artist.
